(SkillCatalog "Codex coding organ: codex-code-status, codex-code-atoms, codex-code-containment-check, codex-code task, codex-code-readonly task, async codex-code-start task, codex-code-readonly-start task, codex-code-jobs, codex-code-job-status job-id, codex-code-result job-id, codex-code-cancel job-id, codex-code-events, codex-code-last-trace")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code task - ask Codex CLI with OpenRouter/Qwen3-Coder-Next to work in the OmegaClaw-Core repo; it may edit files in the repo and returns a traced final message")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-readonly task - ask the same coding organ to inspect/review without writing; use before edits when uncertainty is high")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-start task - start an edit-mode Codex job asynchronously; returns a job id immediately so the loop can continue")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-readonly-start task - start a readonly Codex inspection asynchronously; returns a job id immediately so the loop can continue")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-jobs - list recent async Codex jobs and their states")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-job-status job-id - inspect one async Codex job state")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-result job-id - read the exact result file for a completed async Codex job")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-cancel job-id - ask the membrane to terminate a running async Codex job")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-events - read recent CodexJobStarted/CodexJobComplete event atoms")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-status - check CLI/profile/key readiness without exposing secrets")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-atoms - return symbolic atoms for containment mode, sandbox state, model, profile, working directory, and trace path")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-containment-check - report whether Codex is currently relying on the Codex CLI sandbox or the surrounding VM boundary")
(SkillHelp "codex-code" "codex-code-last-trace - read the most recent coding organ trace")
